==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pending
<hw>Pend"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>pendere</ets> to hang, to be suspended. Cf.
<er>Pendent</er>.]</ety> <def>Not yet decided; in continuance; in
suspension; <as>as, a <ex>pending</ex> suit</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pending</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Pending
<hw>Pend"ing</hw>, <pos>prep.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>During; <as>as,
<ex>pending</ex> the trail</as>.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Until; awaiting; <as>as, no decision will be taken
<ex>pending</ex> his arrival</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pendragon</ent>⟦br⟧
